# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# XPay Exam Portal — Email Configuration
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file and rename it to ".env" (remove .example)
# Then fill in your Gmail credentials below.
#
# HOW TO GET GMAIL APP PASSWORD (FREE, takes 2 minutes):
#
#   STEP 1: Go to https://myaccount.google.com/security
#   STEP 2: Make sure "2-Step Verification" is ON
#           (if not, enable it first — it's free)
#   STEP 3: Go to https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords
#   STEP 4: Click "Create" → name it "XPay Exam Portal"
#   STEP 5: Google shows a 16-character password like: abcd efgh ijkl mnop
#   STEP 6: Copy it (WITHOUT spaces) and paste below as SMTP_PASS
#
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

SMTP_USER=your-gmail@gmail.com
SMTP_PASS=abcdefghijklmnop

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Example (replace with YOUR values):
#   SMTP_USER=jayendra@gmail.com
#   SMTP_PASS=abcdwxyzefghijkl
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
